dBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T03:42:12.000Z","msg":"所以一般餐廳都唔會比員工以身犯險落雨去煮呢道菜"},{"pid":"00e61bc682d705719727d8292a50b9ed62ace25d","tid":778661,"uid":59920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T03:59:04.000Z","msg":"不要再說<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdbb267d252ae644f0f5b6da929dac2e2853d89f","tid":778661,"uid":61464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T04:18:35.000Z","msg":"冇人性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02ee9f9c4bd11cda6babedfd1ace7f96a7b7a0d8","tid":778661,"uid":20032,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T04:20:44.000Z","msg":"下？<br />\n點解落雨唔叫得炒蛋？<br />\n<br />\n有咩問題<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">樓豬滿足未</span></span>"},{"pid":"25a2e30ab39562b5546460535a1d1104138d9425","tid":778661,"uid":30991,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T04:26:51.000Z","msg":"好心唔好開係創意台啦 屌你老母 <br />\n創意分：0 <br />\n好笑都比你地班仆街講到唔好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fef779a4e572e3ba26fdf396e35df19213e9993","tid":778661,"uid":85564,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T04:40:04.000Z","msg":"見你咁白癡就答下你啦<br />\n<br />\n眾所週知 蛋有不同煮法 但最正宗同<br />\n<br />\n最原始既蛋就一定係太陽蛋 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n顧名思義 <br />\n<br />\n呢隻係要太陽下先整到既蛋<br />\n<br />\n 利用太陽既熱力，整熟隻蛋<br />\n<br />\n但之後陸陸續續有其他蛋煮法出現 <br />\n好似炒，蒸等等<br />\n<br />\n炒蛋要用滾油，落雨會有水花<br />\n<br />\n水同油因為磁通量完全唔同<br />\n<br />\n兩者因為粒子性質唔同而彈開<br />\n<br />\n又稱彈油 普通人一掂到輕則毀容<br />\n<br />\n重則甩皮 風險極高 <br />\n<br />\n所以一般餐廳都唔會比員工以身犯險落雨去煮呢道菜<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n有雨落炒蛋供應既餐廳只有少數 而且細佬有幸食過一次<br />\n<br />\n個種回甘真係難以忘懷..."},{"pid":"ef60a8c98fab53a2cf2758dd29e9580a7fbd0bff","tid":778661,"uid":116330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T04:43:16.000Z","msg":"下..落雨仲敢叫炒蛋? 未死過咩"}]}